600
00:20:46,599 --> 00:20:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] sam je bježala od mog poziva.

601
00:20:47,859 --> 00:20:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ja tada nazovem

602
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] evo sestru,

603
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] admiratu,

604
00:20:51,599 --> 00:20:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila tada

605
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] naša provincijska glavarica

606
00:20:54,299 --> 00:20:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] i predstavim se

607
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] i ona kaže

608
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] joj, pa ne mogu vjerovati,

609
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo se baš misli

610
00:20:59,619 --> 00:21:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] šta je s tobom.

611
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:01,839
[SPEAKER_00] I sestre su sjetle

612
00:21:01,839 --> 00:21:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] na večer zajedno.

613
00:21:02,819 --> 00:21:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] One su to meni poslije rekli,

614
00:21:04,619 --> 00:21:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam to poslije shvatila.

615
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] Osmi prvi je bio

616
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] Štadlerov dan.

617
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ja sam,

618
00:21:09,079 --> 00:21:10,319
[SPEAKER_00] to je moj pristanak

619
00:21:10,319 --> 00:21:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] da idem,

620
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] da postanem redovnica

621
00:21:14,539 --> 00:21:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo na njegov spomen dan.

622
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači svakog osmog mjesecu

623
00:21:18,079 --> 00:21:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] sestre obelježavaju

624
00:21:19,579 --> 00:21:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] posebno njegov dan

625
00:21:20,839 --> 00:21:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] i molim mu se.

626
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] I baš na taj dan,

627
00:21:24,319 --> 00:21:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] a ja znači ne znajući,

628
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] još uvijek nisam znala ništa

629
00:21:27,279 --> 00:21:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] o njemu osim

630
00:21:27,839 --> 00:21:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] nekih pojedinosti

631
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] evakvo maleni.

632
00:21:31,099 --> 00:21:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam vrlo brzo se spakirala.

633
00:21:34,539 --> 00:21:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam već 11. prvog bila u Sarajevu.

634
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:39,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazim na kolodvor u četiri ujutro,

635
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ni jednu sestru,

636
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] nikog živog, ne znam.

637
00:21:41,859 --> 00:21:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] I bila sam dva tjedna kod sestara.

638
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ta dva tjedna su bila do tada

639
00:21:48,859 --> 00:21:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] najljepša u mom životu.

640
00:21:50,079 --> 00:21:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] Sestre, znači nisam poznavala ni jednu,

641
00:21:53,779 --> 00:21:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad sam među njima bila,

642
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je zaista,

643
00:21:56,599 --> 00:21:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] koda smo odrasli zajedno,

644
00:21:58,079 --> 00:21:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] koda sam jedna od njih,

645
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] koda smo obitelj,

646
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako to opisati.

647
00:22:03,779 --> 00:22:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon dva tjedna vraćam se kuće u Beć.

648
00:22:06,799 --> 00:22:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] Moji roditelji, svi izvan sebe,

649
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] kakva Bosna, kakav samostan,

650
00:22:11,619 --> 00:22:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] ko ti ispro mozak.

651
00:22:13,039 --> 00:22:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što su oni bili više protiv,

652
00:22:15,579 --> 00:22:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bila više za.

653
00:22:16,539 --> 00:22:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] I opet je uslijedila, naravno,

654
00:22:19,819 --> 00:22:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] jedna borba, jedno bježanje.

655
00:22:22,599 --> 00:22:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] Misliš, nemoguće da je tako savršeno.

656
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoguće, Bože, pa to je sigurno neka zamka zloga.

657
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to može biti da dođem negdje,

658
00:22:30,539 --> 00:22:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] da se tako uklopim među te sestre?

659
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoguće, to je nešto, neka zamka.

660
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon, evo, skoro daljnih devet mjeseci,

661
00:22:40,519 --> 00:22:43,299
[SPEAKER_00] kažem, meni moj duhovnik,

662
00:22:43,299 --> 00:22:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] okej, ne može ovako dalje,

663
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:47,160
[SPEAKER_00] to mora doći kraj tome,

664
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo se mi moli za jedan znak.

665
00:22:48,339 --> 00:22:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, dobro, ajmo se moli za znak.

666
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:52,299
[SPEAKER_00] I ja tada, evo,

667
00:22:52,299 --> 00:22:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] sa njim smo se molili,

668
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] na večer, evo, dođe,

669
00:22:55,759 --> 00:22:58,339
[SPEAKER_00] izvuče mi jedan citat,

670
00:22:58,339 --> 00:23:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže tada, iz prve knjige letopisa,

671
00:23:01,319 --> 00:23:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, tada reče,

672
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] David svojemu sinu Salomonu.

673
00:23:04,539 --> 00:23:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pođi na posao odvažno i smijelo,

674
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,740
[SPEAKER_00] ne boj se i ne plaši se,

675
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] jer Bog, Gospod, Bog moj,

676
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:11,660
[SPEAKER_00] bit će s tobom.

677
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] On te neće ostaviti,

678
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] dok se ne dovrše svi radovi

679
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] za službu u hramu Gospodnjem.

680
00:23:17,980 --> 00:23:21,160
[SPEAKER_00] tada sam zaista u tom trenutku osjetila da je to to.

681
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] I u roku od par dana spakirala svoje stvarčice

682
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] i odšla u Sarajevo.

683
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Relativno brzo,

684
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] nakon, nakon,

685
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] nakon mog dolaska,

686
00:23:30,819 --> 00:23:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] znači, drugog dolaska u Sarajevo,

687
00:23:32,519 --> 00:23:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam dola odlaku da želim pristupiti,

688
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] ali, družbi se stara služak i malog Isusa.

689
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] I tek tada, što bi se rekla,

690
00:23:40,559 --> 00:23:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] evo, tada sam ja tek to osvatila,

691
00:23:42,539 --> 00:23:45,339
[SPEAKER_00] kako me, evo,

692
00:23:45,339 --> 00:23:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] otacu temelitelj doslovce

693
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] od početka do ulazka u samostan pratio,

694
00:23:49,339 --> 00:23:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] taj moj prvi neki,

695
00:23:50,859 --> 00:23:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] da, gospodino je bio 8.1.

696
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:54,359
[SPEAKER_00] jer na njegov spomen,

697
00:23:54,359 --> 00:23:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] došla sam u Bosnu 11.1.

698
00:23:57,059 --> 00:24:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on je 11.1.1882 stupio u Bosnu.

699
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] I na kraju sam, evo,

700
00:24:03,119 --> 00:24:04,680
[SPEAKER_00] ušla službeno u kandidaturu

701
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] moje naše družbe

702
00:24:06,460 --> 00:24:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] na bezgrašno začeće Blažne djevice Marije,

703
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] 8.12. na dan njegovog rađenja za nebo.

704
00:24:13,019 --> 00:24:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista sam bila zatečena,

705
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] nisam mogla vjerovati kako,

706
00:24:20,599 --> 00:24:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] kako gospodin vodi nečiji poziv,

707
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] nečiji život.

708
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] I kad me neko danas pita,

709
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] kako znati koji red,

710
00:24:29,180 --> 00:24:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] kako znati gdje otići,

711
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] onda zaista, ja samo kažem,

712
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] čitajte živote svetaca,

713
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,359
[SPEAKER_00] čitajte o njima,

714
00:24:36,359 --> 00:24:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo gdje te prevuče,

715
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,160
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se ti osjećaš,

716
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,859
[SPEAKER_00] kod kuće, gdje nešto imaš,

717
00:24:40,859 --> 00:24:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] što bi ti štije učiniti,

718
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] tamo idi.

719
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] To će vjerovatno pokazati se ispravnim.

720
00:24:46,579 --> 00:24:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo gdje se čovjek osjeća kod kuće,

721
00:24:48,579 --> 00:24:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] to je ona prava stvar.

722
00:24:51,779 --> 00:24:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, konačno sam i položila

723
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] svoje prve zavijete 2018. godine.

724
00:24:57,799 --> 00:25:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] srstva Jelana imala tada svoje vječne zavijete,

725
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,740
[SPEAKER_00] a ja svoje prve zavijete.

726
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] 2018. godine, o jubilarnoj godini,

727
00:25:04,119 --> 00:25:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] sto te obljetnice preminuća našeg otemelitelja,

728
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je strođenja za nebo.

729
00:25:10,359 --> 00:25:12,680
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujem da je ovo moje svjeročanstvo

730
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] je samo jedno u nizu

731
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] i da druge srstve mogu posljedočiti

732
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] o sličnim iskustvima

733
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] sa našim otemeliteljem.

734
00:25:20,079 --> 00:25:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] On je zaista jedna posebna sobrost,

735
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:25,839
[SPEAKER_00] kao što ćulio se sri Jelene večeras.

736
00:25:25,839 --> 00:25:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] Što više o njemu saznaješ,

737
00:25:28,539 --> 00:25:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] više te zadivljuje njegova ljubav

738
00:25:30,299 --> 00:25:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] i njegova hrabrost

739
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] i silno pouzdanje u Boga koje je on imao.

740
00:25:33,500 --> 00:25:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Imao je jedno junačko srce

741
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] koje je ljubilo majčinskom ljubavi svakoga.

742
00:25:39,279 --> 00:25:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Od kako svojih siroča,

743
00:25:41,579 --> 00:25:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] tako svečenika,

744
00:25:42,619 --> 00:25:44,759
[SPEAKER_00] tako nas svoje duhovne čeri

745
00:25:44,759 --> 00:25:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] i tako svakog čovjeka.

746
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, na kraju bi samo želila vas

747
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] evo, hrabriti, dragi mladi

748
00:25:52,559 --> 00:25:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda tražite još uvijek svoj pozi,

749
00:25:55,599 --> 00:25:56,359
[SPEAKER_00] svoj put,

750
00:25:56,359 --> 00:25:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] da se odvažite živjeti za Krista,

751
00:25:59,519 --> 00:26:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne bojite,

752
00:26:00,519 --> 00:26:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je zaista najljepši život.

753
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi mislimo da ćemo izgubiti svašta nešto

754
00:26:05,559 --> 00:26:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] ako se odvažimo živjeti za njega,

755
00:26:07,339 --> 00:26:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali dobivamo neizmjerno puno više

756
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] i savršenije.

757
00:26:12,119 --> 00:26:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] Od kad sam mu samostavno

758
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] mi je ispunio,

759
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] ma ne ispunio moje želje,

760
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego više nego ono što sam mogla sanjati,

761
00:26:21,599 --> 00:26:23,759
[SPEAKER_00] više nego što sam ja mogla zamisliti.

762
00:26:23,759 --> 00:26:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] I čvrsto se održite naše nebeske majke Marije,

763
00:26:27,859 --> 00:26:29,700
[SPEAKER_00] njoj se utječite svakog dana,

764
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] njezinu bezgrošnom srcu se posvetite.

765
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto moje osobno iskustvo

766
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] i tada ćete vidjeti zaista

767
00:26:35,500 --> 00:26:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] kako se u vama i oko vas mijenja sve nabolje.

768
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] I koje što je rekao jednom svijet Ivan Pavo drugi,

769
00:26:41,859 --> 00:26:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] rekao je kao učinite od svog života remeg dijelo.

770
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što je to učinio i naš otac temelitelj,

771
00:26:48,059 --> 00:26:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] Josip Štadler,

772
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] i mnogi drugi Boži miljenici.

773
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] To želim svima nama i vama.

774
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:56,259
[SPEAKER_00] Nek vas prati Božji blagoslov.

775
00:26:56,259 --> 00:26:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala.

